{"word":"H4998 - נָאָה - nâʼâh - naw-aw' - Be beautiful","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נָאָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>nâʼâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>naw-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be beautiful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழகாயிரு, அலங்காரமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be comely, to be beautiful, to be befitting (Pilpel)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>be at home</i>, that is, (by implication) to be <i>pleasant</i> (or <i>suitable</i>), that is, <i>beautiful: - </i>be beautiful, become, be comely."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4998 - נָאָה - nâʼâh - naw-aw'/4998\">H4998</a>, <a href=\"#/H5000 - נָאוֶה - nâʼveh - naw-veh'/5000\">H5000</a>"}]}